{#
    Gallery: Notifications & flash messages -- Bulma notification colour variants

    Used only when the change is invisible after reload (background jobs, queued emails,
    validation failures). Avoid for obvious info. Anchor: g-notifications.

    Used in:    admin/_gallery/index.html.twig
    Parameters: none
#}
<p class="is-size-7 has-text-grey">
    {{ 'admin_system_gallery.source_of_truth'|trans }}
    admin UX guide ("No flash messages when the result is visible after reload")
</p>

<div class="notification is-success is-light mt-4">
    A success flash message after a queued background job (e.g. emails dispatched).
</div>
<div class="notification is-info is-light">
    An info flash message used sparingly for non-obvious context.
</div>
<div class="notification is-warning is-light">
    A warning flash message - validation passed but with caveats.
</div>
<div class="notification is-danger is-light">
    A danger flash message - the action failed and the page does not show the error inline.
</div>
